<http://drug.uk/usage/pregnancy/7f221110-c6a1-4737-a1e1-e472b468b71c> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " Avoid unless benefit clearly outweighs potential risk—use in the first trimester of pregnancy is associated with a slightly increased risk of major birth defects in the unborn child." .
<http://drug.uk/usage/pregnancy/7f221110-c6a1-4737-a1e1-e472b468b71c> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/Usage> .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/b4420d23-456c-4d1e-8f48-353d8c8d1074> <http://drug.uk/model/patientCondition> "RenalImpairment" .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/b4420d23-456c-4d1e-8f48-353d8c8d1074> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " Dose adjustments\nInitially 75 mg daily and maximum 300 mg daily in 2–3 divided doses if creatinine clearance 30–60 mL/minute.\nInitially 25–50 mg daily and maximum 150 mg daily in 1–2 divided doses if creatinine clearance 15–30 mL/minute.\nInitially 25 mg once daily and maximum 75 mg once daily if creatinine clearance less than 15 mL/minute." .
<http://drug.uk/usage/renal-impairment/b4420d23-456c-4d1e-8f48-353d8c8d1074> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://drug.uk/model/Usage> .
